{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Battle Sablemon! is a singleplayer creature-collection turn-based combat RPG.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/extras/AboutTheGame.png?t=1739377636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect animals blessed with elemental magic in this turn-based, grid-based combat RPG. Train and level up your units or catch new more powerful animals to add to your party!\u00a0 <br><br>Earthquakes and tremors have been felt across Acer Island for weeks now... and the Professor thinks they are supernatural in origin. You and your 2 childhood friends are sent on a journey of discovery across the vast Acer Island, discover the truth of the mysterious tremors all while exploring the various landscapes the island has to offer.\u00a0 <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/extras/SablemonGif2.gif?t=1739377636\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/extras/Features.png?t=1739377636\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Catch Over 100 unique Sablemon</strong> all with their own elements and Talents. Level them up and grow stronger with them over time! Try to collect as many as you can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Complete quests</strong>. Complete quests for the denizens of Acer Island as you discover more and more of the island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize your character</strong>'s clothes and colors. Unlock more clothes through completing tasks, quests and achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Defeat enemy trainers</strong>. Collect Items, coins and more as you battle your way through the island.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/extras/SablemonGif1.gif?t=1739377636\" /><br>*The game is still early in development. Visuals, artwork and screenshots shown are not final.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739377636","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739377636","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/f035b72a82b8f2594de19e7cdfdbc1e7b474eaec/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739377636","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/f035b72a82b8f2594de19e7cdfdbc1e7b474eaec/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739377636","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Battle Sablemon! is a singleplayer creature-collection turn-based combat RPG.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/extras/AboutTheGame.png?t=1739377636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect animals blessed with elemental magic in this turn-based, grid-based combat RPG. Train and level up your units or catch new more powerful animals to add to your party!\u00a0 <br><br>Earthquakes and tremors have been felt across Acer Island for weeks now... and the Professor thinks they are supernatural in origin. You and your 2 childhood friends are sent on a journey of discovery across the vast Acer Island, discover the truth of the mysterious tremors all while exploring the various landscapes the island has to offer.\u00a0 <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417990/extras/SablemonGif2.gif?t=1739377636\" /><br><br><